	   <tr><td colspan=2>Considering FoH has been taking out that part of the Temple, I don't think that this is fake.&nbsp;&nbsp;As a matter of fact, this item is just like all the others -- very, very real.<br><br>My only thought is, some of the melee weapons I saw (Twisted Steel Bastard Sword, was one, I believe) actually have a worse ratio than the Caster items.... that sounds a little crazy.  I'm not saying that casters shouldn't have good ratio -- they should!  But when you've got a same-area of a high level zone dropping a hybrid sword with a ratio around 1.8, and then a caster weapon with a ratio of 1.2..... yet will a hybrid EVER get better, or even equal (at the level) spells that their parent class gets, excepting the Call of Earth, SKy, etc and other rhybrids get?  Even those have no comparison to the spells at the level that their parent class gets...<br><br>Let's take another look into these balancing issues you're always freaking out about, Verant.<br>&nbsp;<br>Menuven Amoray Altruah-Wylt<br>49th Ranger<br>Tribunal</td></tr>
